Job Description:
Scout and screen start-ups from the innovation and emerging industries in Singapore and Asia;
Analyze start-up company information;
Research and perform due diligence on potential innovation programs to identify investment opportunities;
Build and maintain connections with players in the innovation space including incubators and VCs;
Perform other related duties as assigned.
Requirements
Bachelor’s degree in relevant discipline;
Minimum 2-year relevant work experience;
Able to build good relationships with internal and external stakeholders;
Be resourceful and able to work independently;
Good communication and interpersonal skills.
